Introduction

Yukyung (유경) is a South Korean singer under IOK Company. She is the former main dancer, lead vocalist, and visual of the girl group ALICE (formerly known as Elris).
Yukyung auditioned for MixNine but didn’t pass. She specialized in traditional Korean dancing in middle school.

On May 3, 2024, Yukyung announced her departure from ALICE following the expiration of her exclusive contract with IOK Company.
